    <h1>üìä COVID-19 Data Analysis & Visualization</h1>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>üìå Project Overview</h2>
        <p>
            This project focuses on analyzing and visualizing <strong>COVID-19 trends</strong> using
            <strong>Tableau</strong>. The objective is to transform large-scale pandemic data into
            interactive dashboards that provide actionable insights and support data-driven
            decision-making.
        </p>
        <p>
            The analysis includes trend identification, anomaly detection, and time-series modeling
            to extract meaningful patterns from complex datasets.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>üõ†Ô∏è Tools & Technologies</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Tableau</li>
            <li>Statistical Analysis</li>
            <li>Time-Series Analysis (ARIMA)</li>
            <li>Data Visualization</li>
            <li>Interactive Dashboards</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>üìÇ Dataset</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Dataset size: ~500,000+ records</li>
            <li>Contains COVID-19 case trends and related metrics</li>
            <li>Data was cleaned, transformed, and optimized prior to visualization</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>üîç Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Interactive dashboards</strong> for trend analysis</li>
            <li><strong>Statistical methods:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Correlation analysis</li>
                    <li>Rolling averages</li>
                    <li>Forecasting models</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Advanced analytics:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Anomaly detection</li>
                    <li>Clustering</li>
                    <li>ARIMA time-series decomposition (trend & seasonality)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Optimized data processing:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Raw data scripting</li>
                    <li>Volumetric conversion</li>
                    <li>Inner joins</li>
                    <li>Calculated fields</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Improved usability:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Dashboard navigation actions</li>
                    <li>Dynamic parameters for user control</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>üéØ Outcomes</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Converted complex COVID-19 data into clear, actionable insights</li>
            <li>Enabled executive-level decision support through visual storytelling</li>
            <li>Improved dashboard usability and analytical efficiency</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

